* [[Thunder Airlines]] - Beechcraft A100 King Air; [[Cessna 208|Cessna 208B Grand Caravan]]; and [[Mitsubishi MU-2]] from [[Thunder Bay International Airport]], [[Sudbury Airport]] and [[Timmins/Victor M. Power Airport]]

* [[Flightexec]] at [[Toronto/Buttonville Municipal Airport]] and [[London International Airport]]

* [[SkyCare Air Ambulance]] operating two [[Fairchild Swearingen Metroliner]] aircraft at [[Sioux Lookout Airport]].

* [[Air Bravo]] operating Pilatus PC-12 aircraft out of [[Timmins]], [[Sioux Lookout]], [[Elliot Lake]], and [[Lake Simcoe Regional Airport]].

